  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/ee72290035f276c7351168b81fbf57a0.webp?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/2a5d907e079753a69401244b6ad47f0d.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/2a5d907e079753a69401244b6ad47f0d.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/2a5d907e079753a69401244b6ad47f0d.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Changing terrain is your main weapon now</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/38807d14a16fe644132e2a5441b0301e.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/38807d14a16fe644132e2a5441b0301e.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/38807d14a16fe644132e2a5441b0301e.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Changing units, is <span class=\"bb_strike\">your sidearm</span> very helpful too</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You are not a general - you are a GOD.</strong><br>No need to bark orders at troops - instead, reshape the land itself: raise mountains, flood the valleys, and bend the battlefield to your will. Because you can.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget traditional commands - here, <strong>your divine influence controls the tide of battle.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛠 Gameplay Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100% Predictable Combat</strong> - No RNG. Plan everything in advance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Indirect Unit Control</strong> - Units move on their own, following fixed pathfinding rules.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terraform the Battlefield</strong> - Your powers let you reshape terrain and even alter unit classes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite Replayability</strong> - Build a unique deck of spells and units on every run. Unlock new heroes with different starting styles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/22260a1a21333109e43fd53967636f56.webp?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/b35c7afc17efeca2a86e3f63c96d5e45.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/b35c7afc17efeca2a86e3f63c96d5e45.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/b35c7afc17efeca2a86e3f63c96d5e45.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/a26f72b83847378b8b3a9ebcbcf62de2.webp?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/5e3eb35ddb3eb0c649e84d40c01a9a84.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/5e3eb35ddb3eb0c649e84d40c01a9a84.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/5e3eb35ddb3eb0c649e84d40c01a9a84.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/cc37c8300784dc014697deefff0f636b.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/cc37c8300784dc014697deefff0f636b.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/cc37c8300784dc014697deefff0f636b.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(*) 0% random actually means 0% output randomness in the core game. You may still experience input randomness in the core game, as well as various types of randomness between battles. Consult your numerologist before using this product.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/ee72290035f276c7351168b81fbf57a0.webp?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/2a5d907e079753a69401244b6ad47f0d.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/2a5d907e079753a69401244b6ad47f0d.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/2a5d907e079753a69401244b6ad47f0d.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Changing terrain is your main weapon now</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/38807d14a16fe644132e2a5441b0301e.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/38807d14a16fe644132e2a5441b0301e.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/38807d14a16fe644132e2a5441b0301e.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Changing units, is <span class=\"bb_strike\">your sidearm</span> very helpful too</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You are not a general - you are a GOD.</strong><br>No need to bark orders at troops - instead, reshape the land itself: raise mountains, flood the valleys, and bend the battlefield to your will. Because you can.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget traditional commands - here, <strong>your divine influence controls the tide of battle.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛠 Gameplay Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100% Predictable Combat</strong> - No RNG. Plan everything in advance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Indirect Unit Control</strong> - Units move on their own, following fixed pathfinding rules.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terraform the Battlefield</strong> - Your powers let you reshape terrain and even alter unit classes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelite Replayability</strong> - Build a unique deck of spells and units on every run. Unlock new heroes with different starting styles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/22260a1a21333109e43fd53967636f56.webp?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/b35c7afc17efeca2a86e3f63c96d5e45.poster.avif?t=1769700503\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/b35c7afc17efeca2a86e3f63c96d5e45.webm?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/b35c7afc17efeca2a86e3f63c96d5e45.mp4?t=1769700503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877650/extras/a26f72b83847378b8b3a9ebcbcf62de2.webp?t=1769700503\" width=616 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"